    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_10_1847-1889",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1847-1889",
      "markText": "教士越多地远离与他们同时垮台的那些东西时，教会力量就逐渐恢复并更深地扎根于人们心中。",
      "totalCount": 828,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1847&rangeEnd=1889",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1847&rangeEnd=1889"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_9_4428-4488",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4428-4488",
      "markText": "不久以后，就很难做到这些，因为伟大革命一旦成功，就会令激发革命的原因消失，而且由于革命本身那么成功，会使其变得难以解释。",
      "totalCount": 748,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4428&rangeEnd=4488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4428&rangeEnd=4488"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_65_4243-4257",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "4243-4257",
      "markText": "追求大自由，就会陷入大奴役！",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=4243&rangeEnd=4257",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=4243&rangeEnd=4257"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_11_2542-2595",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2542-2595",
      "markText": "欲让此类学说转化为革命行动，必须是社会条件、风俗习惯发生了某些变化，为人们在心理上接受革命学说做好了铺垫。",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2542&rangeEnd=2595",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2542&rangeEnd=2595"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_11_2731-2800",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2731-2800",
      "markText": "法国大革命最令人瞩目的，不在于采取的手段，不在于提出的思想，而在于如此之多的人们，能够如此有效地采用那些手段，如此快速地欣然接受那些思想。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2731&rangeEnd=2800",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2731&rangeEnd=2800"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_62_6001-6066",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "6001-6066",
      "markText": "倘若不再通过阶层等级、家族行会等纽带而凝聚在一起，人们就会只考虑自己，就会只关心私利，就会只蜷缩于无视公共美德的狭隘个人主义之中。",
      "totalCount": 525,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=6001&rangeEnd=6066",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=6001&rangeEnd=6066"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_10_1546-1580",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1546-1580",
      "markText": "人们如此仇恨基督教，并非因为它是一种宗教，而是因为它是一种政治制度；",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1546&rangeEnd=1580",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1546&rangeEnd=1580"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_11_1031-1076",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1031-1076",
      "markText": "一切外战都有内战色彩，一切内战都有外人插手；为新利益而忘却旧利益，以道义问题取代领土问题。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1031&rangeEnd=1076",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1031&rangeEnd=1076"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_63_7094-7136",
      "chapterUid": 63,
      "range": "7094-7136",
      "markText": "贵族不再负责上述事情时，贵族特权带来的负担就显得更沉重，甚至贵族本身的存在也成疑问。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=63&rangeStart=7094&rangeEnd=7136",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=63&rangeStart=7094&rangeEnd=7136"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_10_858-938",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "858-938",
      "markText": "有些人认为，藐视上帝，乃赎买当初对政府小吏唯唯诺诺的罪过；他们抛弃了大革命信条中最自由、最高贵、最自豪的一切，并自欺欺人认为，只要不信教，就仍然忠于大革命精神。",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=858&rangeEnd=938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=858&rangeEnd=938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_25_2142-2221",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "2142-2221",
      "markText": "令人遗憾的是，人们不是将贵族置于法律约束之下，而是将贵族打翻在地并斩草除根。这一错误，是从国民躯体中割除了必不可少的部分，给自由留下了一道永远难以弥合的伤口。",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=2142&rangeEnd=2221",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=2142&rangeEnd=2221"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_62_5879-5913",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "5879-5913",
      "markText": "长期以来一直最难摆脱专制的，恰恰是那些从未以及无法存在贵族制度的社会",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=5879&rangeEnd=5913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=5879&rangeEnd=5913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_55_1068-1092",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "1068-1092",
      "markText": "只要平等与专制相结合，人们的心智水准就会永远下降",
      "totalCount": 429,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=1068&rangeEnd=1092",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=1068&rangeEnd=1092"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_10_3844-3869",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "3844-3869",
      "markText": "总之，法国大革命，既是他们的灾难，又是他们的导师。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3844&rangeEnd=3869",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3844&rangeEnd=3869"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_16_7027-7102",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "7027-7102",
      "markText": "御前会议认为某地不适宜种植某种作物，就会发布禁种令。有的法令，竟然要求拔掉在其认为土质低劣的地上种植的葡萄。由此可见，当时政府已由统治者转变为监护人。",
      "totalCount": 392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=7027&rangeEnd=7102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=7027&rangeEnd=7102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_68_6260-6291",
      "chapterUid": 68,
      "range": "6260-6291",
      "markText": "经验告诉我们，就坏政府而言，最危险之时，往往就是着手改革之际。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=68&rangeStart=6260&rangeEnd=6291",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=68&rangeStart=6260&rangeEnd=6291"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_58_3635-3658",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "3635-3658",
      "markText": "由此可见，历史乃画廊：在那里，真品少、赝品多。",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3635&rangeEnd=3658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3635&rangeEnd=3658"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_63_484-515",
      "chapterUid": 63,
      "range": "484-515",
      "markText": "因此，遭受中世纪制度压迫最轻之地，却成为最难以忍受该制度之地。",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=63&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=515",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=63&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=515"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103182_67_4372-4456",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "4372-4456",
      "markText": "在他们看来，中国令人心驰神往、叹为观止，盖其君主不抱偏见，年年岁岁举行亲耕礼，奖掖有用之术；中国的一切官员，均通过科举选拔任用；中国只把哲学视为宗教，只把文人奉为贵族。",
      "totalCount": 368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103182&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=4372&rangeEnd=4456",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2f932450813ab8eceg01272c?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=4372&rangeEnd=4456"
    }
